title: [Lower Trollfang, Clearing]
description: A foul stench floats heavily on the air here, almost causing you to retch.  You are led to assume the source is a ramshackle hut which lies to the east, its poor condition a stark contrast both to the other huts nearby and to the impressive and finely sculpted temple which hovers near.
paths: Obvious paths: northeast, southeast, south, northwest
